<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="05 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的音樂風格，<delay8 />
有時候是源自<delay8 /><tag a="135" b="4" arg="0xcd00" />，
有時候是<tag a="135" b="4" arg="0xcd01" />的延伸<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />除此之外，<delay8 />
還有一些書影響到<delay8 />
身為藝術家的<tag a="110" b="10" />呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />》。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從中能學到很多東西，<delay8 />所以也推薦你讀喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會送花給女孩子，<delay20 />
或許也是受到這本書的影響吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然世上並不存在<delay20 />
藝術家的明確定義啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但只要透過藝術與創作<delay8 />
來表達自我，<delay20 />應該就能如此稱呼了吧？
我是這麼想的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我也是<delay8 />
飾演<tag a="110" b="10" />這個角色的<delay40 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一位藝術家！</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="0" arg="0x2 0x3" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="0" arg="0x9 0xa" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你會送哪種花<delay20 />
給重要的人呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />玫瑰的花語會隨著花色跟數量而改變，<delay20 />
所以有可能因為預料之外的花語<delay8 />
而傷害到對方。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，我認為最重要的是<delay20 />
對方收到禮物是否開心，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且為他人煩惱的時間<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也是非常珍貴的時間呢。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就聽聽<delay20 />我的煩惱吧，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不，<delay20 />其實也不是什麼嚴重的問題。<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但這種事我也只能和你談，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能理解我的想法的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦，<delay8 />奇怪？<delay40 />
我忘記自己在煩惱什麼了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />
或許你真的有這種<delay8 />
不可思議的力量呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="012" attrib="0d 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了維持<tag a="110" b="10" />的風格，<delay20 />
我對於時下流行，<delay8 />
總是密切關心。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而最近<delay8 />特別在意的是<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0xe 0xf 0x10" /></message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是緊身牛仔褲喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種緊貼著軀體的設計，<delay20 />
可以完美呈現出<delay8 />
腳的線條跟腿型呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />特別是如果讓女性穿上，<delay20 />
看起來應該會很美吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是破洞牛仔褲！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />裂開的洞，是穿著者的個性<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正因為誰都無法模仿，<delay20 />
所以才能說得上是獨一無二吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是如果野性過頭的話，<delay20 />
可是會被女孩子討厭的，<delay8 />
需要多加注意呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是寬褲！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然這要高手才能靈活搭配，<delay8 />
但能順便享受打扮足部的樂趣喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過說歸說，<delay8 />
我本身是不穿鞋子的啦！<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈！</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="2" arg="0x15 0x16 0x17 0x18" /></message>
	<message label="019" attrib="12 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我問你喔，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />你喜歡多長的褲子？</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />褲子的長度啊，<delay20 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />越是縮短，<delay20 />
就越能吸引周圍的熱情視線喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以非常短的褲子<delay20 />
才會被稱為「熱褲」。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />順便一提，<delay20 />
你也讓我覺得很熱喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />說笑的啦！<delay8 />哈哈！</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有種打扮風格，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是穿上長長的褲子，<delay8 />
再捲起褲管露出腳踝。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />但是如果捲過頭了，<delay20 />
看來又會很土氣<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且又聽說<delay8 />
七分褲短到像熱褲的話，<delay20 />
就會被女孩子討厭<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />算了，<delay8 />到頭來，<delay20 />
還是普通最好呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />故意跟時代背道而馳，<delay20 />
用長版衣物來營造老派風格，<delay20 />
你這樣也很帥呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我喜歡像你這種<delay20 />
不被潮流擺布的人！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我還是覺得<delay20 />自然才是最棒的！<delay40 />
<anim id="Grin" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />也就是宛如初生的樣子<delay8 />…<delay8 />…<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="026" attrib="1b 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
我來教你怎麼鼓起勇氣吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="027" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x1c 0x1d 0x1e" /></message>
	<message label="028" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是回想珍愛之人的笑容。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要擁有必須守護的存在，<delay20 />
就會讓人變得無比強悍呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="029" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是別想太多，<delay20 />
先試著行動！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />無論結果如何<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我都會讚賞<delay8 />
勇於挑戰的人！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之先想像「成功」的狀況，<delay20 />
然後一頭栽進去吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比起束手旁觀而後悔，<delay20 />
不如放手一搏再後悔，<delay8 />
這樣健康多了吧？<tag a="110" b="6" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使<delay8 />留下了令人扼腕的結果<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一定<delay8 />也會以你為榮！</message>
	<message label="032" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="032_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Étoile<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
那是所有舞者的夢想，<delay20 />
也就是萬人追捧的首席舞者<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我不能一直這樣滿足於自我陶醉，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也得得到其他人的認同才行<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請你幫忙不著痕跡地放出消息吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如說，「這座<tag a="110" b="9" />上<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像有位舉世聞名的舞者喔！」<delay20 />
之類的～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="032_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
自從來到<tag a="110" b="8" />，<delay20 />
就不再過著被時間追趕的日子，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在早晨的陽光下醒來，<delay20 />聽蟲鳴辨別四季，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在這種生活中找到了自己的步調，<delay20 />
也找到了真正的自我。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />人只要從時間的束縛中被解放，<delay20 />
搞不好反而能活得更規律呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你一定也能找到的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真正的自我！</message>
	<message label="034" attrib="23 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊，在一個人獨處的時候，<delay20 />
常常會獨自思考著<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />五年之後，<delay20 />甚至是十年後的事呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="035" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x24 0x25 0x26" /></message>
	<message label="036" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到時候，這裡的風景<delay20 />　
也肯定會變得不一樣了吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是，不管時代如何改變，<delay20 />
我們兩人永遠都會是朋友喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我說的沒錯吧，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />？</message>
	<message label="037" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到時候，我們也會跟著成長，<delay20 />　
然後變成現在的我們<delay20 />
所無法想像的樣子吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但就算外表不同，<delay20 />
我們兩人仍有堅定的情誼相繫著彼此。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我說的沒錯吧，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />？</message>
	<message label="038" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />將來究竟會發生什麼事呢？<delay20 />
我們也無從得知<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但只有一件事請不要忘記。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />對我來說，<delay20 />
是位無可取代的，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />永遠的好朋友喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="041" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 0a"><tag a="60" b="13" arg="0x2a 0x2b 0x2c 0x2d" /></message>
	<message label="042" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一旦進入這個季節，<delay20 />
就會有很多人展開新生活呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也來試著開始做些什麼好了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是尋找自我的旅行之類的？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />挑戰新事物永遠不嫌晚，<delay20 />就算那是
被認為現在做已經太晚的事情也一樣。</message>
	<message label="043" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在海邊或河邊釣魚，<delay20 />
還有潛水接觸海洋生物，<delay20 />
說到夏天就是玩水喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓自己嗨起來，<delay20 />
展現和平時不同的一面吧！<10_4 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯，靠著名為夏天的魔法<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="044" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />進入秋季後，這座島也開始<delay20 />
吹起令人心情舒暢的風呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />吹著如此舒適的風悠閒地度過，<delay20 />
就算是漫長的秋夜，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也一下子就過去了。</message>
	<message label="045" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道為什麼雪是白色的嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是因為它忘了自身的顏色喔……</message>
</msbt>